[[The Obligatory Pirate's Cove]] is on [[The Mysterious Island of Mystery]]. It be full of pirates of every description. At least, descriptions that starrrt with S and end in y.

If your main stat isn't high enough, you'll see the following message:
:As you approach the Obligatory Pirates' Cove, a slouchy pirate jumps out from behind a bush.
:"Avast ye," he says.
:He's a lot bigger than you, so you avast with a quickness.
<center>(You must have at least 45 $Stat to adventure here.)</center>

These pirates are only friendly to those who know how to dress properly. So, put on your [[Swashbuckling Getup]] or pin on your [[pirate fledges]] and you'll able to [[The Obligatory Pirate's Cove (in disguise)|fully explore]] the Cove.

